{"id":58400,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/04/公民社会与ngo发展周刊（99）/","date":"2010-04-15T06:30:03Z","modified":"2010-09-24T18:53:39Z","title":"冉云飞：公民社会与NGO发展周刊（99）","content":"<div>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><strong><span>本期特别关注：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">1</span></span><span>：中国旱灾调查；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">2</span></span><span>：打压</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">NGO</span></span><span>后果严重；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">3</span></span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">2009</span></span><span>年慈善捐赠报告；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">4</span></span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">NGO</span></span><span>组织如何利用互联网募款。</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span>我一直重申的是：欢迎各</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">NGO</span></span><span>组织和有心人提供诸种信得过的信息，每条信息的真伪，请实际参与者进一步自行核实。请注意，我不直接接受任何捐款和财物，我也不负责钱物的中转工作，我只负责给各位牵线搭桥。我的工作邮箱是</span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://newdesai.appspot.com/?url=aGNyS%2BKE%5E4R%5Extg.Pz5YcesP%60R6wpoL8%3Am%5C-%5CLr%40t%5BnLyKxu%5CV.%3FNoUqMvv%5Dj%5BzRe%2CfFABZNRH%2C7%3ER2q%5DV5gHd%3E%5D%3ErO%3E\">lijuhantian@sina.com</a> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span><strong>一：中国旱灾真相调查。</strong>感谢时寒冰先生精细的分析，以及出色的实地考察。中国的灾难大多如他所说：“一分天灾，九分人祸”。各级政府的短视和贪腐，正使微小的天灾变成巨大的灾难，成为整个中国社会爆发危机的火药桶。如不在制度和技术上加以改进，要想扼制目前各方面溃烂的局面，绝非易事。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">1</span></span><span>）：时寒冰：《旱灾真相实地调查（上）》</span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\"> </span><span>“我实地调查得出的结果是：西南干旱，一分天灾，九分人祸”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://shihb.blog.sohu.com/148258905.html\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://shihb.blog.sohu.com/148258905.html</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">2</span></span><span>）：时寒冰：云南抗旱救灾感悟（含</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">44</span></span><span>张照片）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://shihb.blog.sohu.com/148038079.html\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://shihb.blog.sohu.com/148038079.html</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">3</span></span><span>）：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">“</span></span><span>低碳救灾</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">” </span></span><span>为了更美好的明天</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">——</span></span><span>绿色和平在灾区：装设太阳能水泵。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.greenpeace.org/china/zh/news/drought-solar-story\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://www.greenpeace.org/china/zh/news/drought-solar-story</span></a></span><span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><strong><span>二：萧瀚：刁难打击</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">NGO </span></span><span>终将严重破坏稳定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://business.sohu.com/20100412/n271447359.shtml\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://business.sohu.com/20100412/n271447359.shtml</span></a></span><span>。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">NGO</span></span><span>是一个社会得以良好发展的助推器和粘合剂，世界上没有任何一个政府无所不能，即令你将所有的权力和资源都掌握在手中，你对社会的管理都不是全能的。缺少</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">NGO</span></span><span>良性发展的社会，那么这个社会的创造力、活力都将会受到极大的制约，阶层对立、贫富悬隔将不可能得到有效的解决。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span><strong>三：一个拒绝理想的社会是可怕的。</strong>当下中国没有信仰，没有普世价值观，只有金钱至上、利益万能，实用主义雷同到令人伤心的地步，这绝对不是一个健康的社会所当有。所有不违宪不违法的理想，都应该给予尝试的机会，这个社会才有未来。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">1</span></span><span>）：创造一个不拒绝“理想”的社会。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.npi.org.cn/newsshow.php?pid=747\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://www.npi.org.cn/newsshow.php?pid=747</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">2</span></span><span>）：陈文茜：这里从不拒绝有理想的人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_5325f6eb0100f17g.html\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_5325f6eb0100f17g.html</span></a></span><span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><strong><span>四：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">2009</span></span><span>年慈善捐赠报告发布</span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\"> </span><span>四成善款流向教育领域。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://edu.ifeng.com/news/detail_2010_04/09/516301_0.shtml\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://edu.ifeng.com/news/detail_2010_04/09/516301_0.shtml</span></a></span></strong><span><strong>。</strong>这样的慈善报告由官方做出，除了数据粗糙乃至做假以外，还从反面证明了公民社会的孱弱，以及</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">NGO</span></span><span>组织被官方打压的残酷现实。慈善捐项的透明、款项的实施、慈善组织的公信力，都是目前慈善捐赠的大问题。当然最大的问题就是政府对慈善的高度垄断和可怕控制。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span><strong>五：灾后重建及其它招募和需求。（</strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">1</span></span><span>）：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">[</span></span><span>截至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">4.25]</span></span><span>梁漱溟乡村建设中心西南抗旱志愿者招募倡议书。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.chinadevelopmentbrief.org.cn/sortinfoview.php?id=2040\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://www.chinadevelopmentbrief.org.cn/sortinfoview.php?id=2040</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">2</span></span><span>）：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">[</span></span><span>上海</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">]</span></span><span>壹基金之家网站招聘多个职位（截至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">5.31</span></span><span>）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.99doing.com/zhichang/show.php?itemid=7919\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://www.99doing.com/zhichang/show.php?itemid=7919</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">3</span></span><span>）：双肩背上的流动儿童图书馆志愿者招募书。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.greengo.cn/news.php?id=5453\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://www.greengo.cn/news.php?id=5453</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">4</span></span><span>）：北京农民之子文化发展中心招募二手店</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">/</span></span><span>图书馆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">/</span></span><span>幼儿园志愿者。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.chinadevelopmentbrief.org.cn/sortinfoview.php?id=2018\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://www.chinadevelopmentbrief.org.cn/sortinfoview.php?id=2018</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">5</span></span><span>）：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">[</span></span><span>北京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">]</span></span><span>全球消除贫困联盟</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">&#8211;</span></span><span>中国（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">GCAP-China</span></span><span>）招聘协调员。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.99doing.com/zhichang/show.php?itemid=7831\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://www.99doing.com/zhichang/show.php?itemid=7831</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">6</span></span><span>）：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">[</span></span><span>截至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">4.30]</span></span><span>欢迎申请世界保护监测中心保护领导者一年硕士。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.chinadevelopmentbrief.org.cn/sortinfoview.php?id=2043\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://www.chinadevelopmentbrief.org.cn/sortinfoview.php?id=2043</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">7</span></span><span>）：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">[</span></span><span>北京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">]</span></span><span>泓德中育教育机构诚聘项目官员和项目助理各</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">2</span></span><span>名。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.99doing.com/zhichang/show.php?itemid=7777\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://www.99doing.com/zhichang/show.php?itemid=7777</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">8</span></span><span>）：社区伙伴招聘项目官员。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.gsean.org/plus/view.php?aid=5403\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://www.gsean.org/plus/view.php?aid=5403</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">9</span></span><span>）：<span style=\"color: black;\"> 有爱有益行</span></span><span style=\"color: black;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">—</span></span><span style=\"color: black;\">云南益行工作组紧急招募救灾备灾相关志愿者（长期）。</span><span style=\"color: black;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://bbs.city.tianya.cn/tianyacity/Content/62/1/552342.shtml\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://bbs.city.tianya.cn/tianyacity/Content/62/1/552342.shtml</span></a></span><span style=\"color: black;\">。</span><span style=\"color: black;\" lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\"> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span><strong>六：灾后重建及其它诸种信息汇集。（</strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">1</span></span><span>）：灾区居民自拍社区故事项目</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">3</span></span><span>月简报。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.512ngo.org.cn/news_detail.asp?id=2186\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://www.512ngo.org.cn/news_detail.asp?id=2186</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">2</span></span><span>）：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">70%</span></span><span>的受调查中国城市网民参与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">“</span></span><span>地球一小时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">”</span></span><span>。</span><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.wwfchina.org/wwfpress/presscenter/pressdetail.shtm?id=1026\"><span style=\"color: #800080;\">http://www.wwfchina.org/wwfpress/presscenter/pressdetail.shtm?id=1026</span></a></span></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">3</span></span><span>）：壹基金西南抗旱一线。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.onefoundation.cn/html/98/n-1098.html\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://www.onefoundation.cn/html/98/n-1098.html</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">4</span></span><span>）：郭虹：再访台湾。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.512ngo.org.cn/news_detail.asp?id=2187\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; color: #800080;\">http://www.512ngo.org.cn/news_detail.asp?id=2187</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman;\">5</span></span><span>）：</span><span style=\"color: black;\" lang=\"ZH\">文新</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: black;\" lang=\"EN-US\">83</span><span style=\"color: black;\" lang=\"ZH\">第一次慈善拍卖活动总汇</span><span style=\"color: black;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: black;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://wen.xin83.blog.163.com/blog/static/13163962020103503112441/\"><span style=\"color: #800080;\">http://wen.xin83.blog.163.com/blog/static/13163962020103503112441/</span></a></span><span style=\"color: black;